        {
            "title": "美伊和談停滯推升歐洲天然氣價格",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週三歐洲天然氣價格走高,投資者注意到美國與伊朗之間的和平談判幾乎沒有取得突破的跡象,而這可能導致<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>重新開放。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間08:41(格林威治標準時間12:41),根據洲際交易所數據,荷蘭TTF樞紐基準近月合約上漲1.81歐元至45.40歐元/兆瓦時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《華爾街日報》週二報導,美國總統唐納德·川普已指示助手為對伊朗的長期封鎖做準備,這標誌著華盛頓在權衡下一步行動時轉向持續的經濟施壓。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-aba266db-1b7e-3411-a3f9-adcd95d81d33-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報導援引美國官員稱,川普選擇加強扼制伊朗石油出口的努力,並限制進出其港口的航運,認為封鎖比恢復大規模軍事打擊或尋求快速外交退出的風險更小。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉是在4月停火之後採取的,當時停火結束了一場大規模轟炸行動,但該地區的緊張局勢仍然高漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》表示,川普最近拒絕了伊朗提出的三步驟提案,該提案將儘早解除荷莫茲海峽的封鎖,同時推遲核談判,川普認為該提案不足以滿足美國對德黑蘭核計劃限制的要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導補充稱,川普不願放棄一項關鍵要求,即伊朗承諾暫停鈾濃縮活動至少20年,並接受該期限之後的限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷莫茲海峽實際上處於關閉狀態,這條重要水道承載著全球約五分之一的液化天然氣流量,已引發能源衝擊。在此背景下,TTF價格仍遠高於2月下旬戰爭開始前的水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%87%E5%81%9C%E6%BB%AF%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%87%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-140235749.html",
